headline: Resmed Announces Participation in the Bank of America Global Healthcare Conference 2025
summary: SAN DIEGO, Sept. 16, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Resmed (NYSE: RMD, ASX: RMD) today announced Mick Farrell, chairman and chief executive officer, and Dr. Carlos Nunez, chief medical officer, will present at the Bank of America Global Healthcare Conference 2025 on Tuesday, September 23, 2025, beginning at approximately 1:20 p.m. (British Summer Time) in London. More information about this event, including access to the live, audio-only webcast, may be accessed by visiting https://investor.resmed.com
